msgid "Further Options"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:86
msgid "Merge Limit"
msgstr "合并限度"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:86
msgid ""
"The maximum distance between a vertex and its mirror copy before they are "
"merged together. In other words, a vertex may be half this distance away from "
"the mirror plane before it snaps to it."
msgstr ""
"顶点与其镜像副本在合并到一起前，它们之间的最大距离。换言之，顶点在吸附到镜面上"
"前，可以离镜面有一半的该距离。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:93
msgid "Mirror Object"
msgstr "镜像物体"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:89
msgid ""
"An :ref:`Object Selector <ui-eye-dropper>` to select an object (usually an "
"empty), to be used as the reference for the mirror process: its center and axes "
"will drive the plane(s) of symmetry. You can of course animate its position/"
"rotation to animate the mirror effect."
msgstr ""
"选择物体(通常是空物体)的 :ref:`物体选择器 <ui-eye-dropper>` ，供镜像过程参考：其"
"中心和轴将沿着平面（一个或多个）作对称。你当然可以修改其位置/旋转属性，以观看动"
"态的镜面效果。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:96
msgid "Hints"
msgstr "提示"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:98
msgid ""
"Many modeling tasks involve creating objects that are symmetrical. However, "
"there used to be no quick way to model both halves of an object without using "
"one of the workarounds that have been discovered by clever Blender artists over "
"the years. A common technique was to model one half of an object and use :kbd:"
"`Alt-D` to create a linked duplicate which can then be scaled on one axis by -1 "
"to produce a perfect mirror-image copy which updates in real-time as you edit."
msgstr ""
"很多建模任务都涉及到创建对称的物体。然而，在没有被聪明的Blender艺术家多年来发现"
"了一种变通方案之前，过去没有快速建模对象两半的方法。一个常见的​​技巧是建模一半物"
"体，然后使用 :kbd:`Alt-D` 创建链接副本，随后可以通过在其中一个轴上缩放 ``-1`` 以"
"产生完美的镜像副本，它可以在你编辑的时候实时更新。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:104
msgid ""
"The Mirror Modifier offers a simpler way to do this. Once your modeling is "
"completed you can either click *Apply* to make a real version of your mesh or "
"leave it as-is for future editing."
msgstr ""
"镜像修改器提供了一个简单的方法来做到这一点。一旦你建模完成后，可以点击 *应用*，"
"观看网面的真实版本，或者保持不变，以供将来编辑。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:109
msgid "Using the Mirror Modifier with a Subdivision Surface Modifier"
msgstr "镜像修改器与细分表面修改器的配合使用"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:111
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When using the Mirror Modifier along with a :doc:`Subdivision Surface </"
"modeling/modifiers/generate/subsurf>` modifier, the order in which the "
"modifiers are placed is important."
msgstr ""
"镜像修改器同 :doc:`细分表面 </modifiers/generate/subsurf>` 修改器一起使用时，其"
"中，修改器的顺序很重要。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:118
#, fuzzy
msgid "Subdivision Surface Modifier before Mirror Modifier."
msgstr "细分表面修改器在镜像修改器之前"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:120
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The above image shows the Subdivision Surface Modifier placed before the Mirror "
"one; as you can see the effect of this is that the mesh is split down the "
"center line of the mirror effect. This is because the Subdivision calculation "
"moves vertices away from the mirror plane, too far away from the *Merge Limit*."
msgstr ""
"上图显示了细分表面修改器置于镜面修改器前的效果；你可以看到这样的效果，网面沿着中"
"心线分割的镜像效果。这是因为，细分表面修改器的计算移动顶点远离镜面，远在 *合并限"
"度* 之外。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:128
#, fuzzy
msgid "Mirror Modifier before Subdivision Surface Modifier."
msgstr "镜像修改器在细分表面修改器之前"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:130
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The above image shows the Mirror Modifier placed before the Subdivision Surface "
"Modifier. In this order, the mirror calculation is done and the vertices are "
"merged together. Only after that does the Subdivision Surface Modifier move any "
"vertices."
msgstr ""
"上图显示了镜像修改器置于细分表面修改器之前的效果。在此顺序里，镜像的计算完成后，"
"顶点被合并在一起。只有在那之后，细分表面修改器会移动任何顶点。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:136
msgid "Accurately Positioning the Mirror Plane"
msgstr "精确定位镜面"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:138
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To apply a Mirror Modifier, it is common to have to move the object's center "
"onto the edge or face that is to be the axis for mirroring. This can be tricky "
"when attempted visually."
msgstr ""
"应用镜像修改器之前，需要移动物体的中心到边或面，以此作为镜像的轴。视觉上尝试时难"
"以捉摸。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:142
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A good technique to achieve an exact position is to select the edge, then use :"
"kbd:`Shift-S` and choosing *Cursor to Selection*. This will position the 3D "
"Cursor in the center of the edge. Finally, press :kbd:`Shift-Ctrl-Alt-C` for "
"the *Set Origin* menu, then select *Origin to 3D Cursor*. This will move the "
"object's center (and thus, the mirror plane) to where the 3D cursor is located, "
"and the mirroring will be exact."
msgstr ""
"完成精准定位的一个好技巧是选择边，然后使用 :kbd:`Shift-S` 并选择 *移动光标到选择"
"* 。这将在边的中心放置3D光标。最后，按下 :kbd:`Ctrl-Alt-Shift-C` 唤出 *设置原点"
"* 菜单，然后选择 *移动原点到3D光标*。这将移动物体的中心（也就是镜面）到3D光标的"
"位置，镜像操作将是精准的。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/generate/mirror.rst:150
msgid ""
"An alternative is to use an Empty as a *Mirror Object* that you move to the "
"correct position."
msgstr "另一种方法是使用一个空物体，作为你移动到正确位置的 *镜物体*。"
